        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>ceramic glaze by composition or origin [300015094], ceramic glaze [300015092], glaze (coating by location) [300015091], coating by location or context [300015089], coating (material) [300014907], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
